
Installation (ubuntu 18.04 LTS)
1. set QMMMWsoftware to $HOME
  e.g., finally,
  $HOME/QMMMWsoftware
2. cd $HOME/QMMMWsoftware
3. chmod +x ./install.sh
4. ./install.sh

Test
1. cd $HOME/QMMMWsoftware/tests
2. ./run_32water_mc.sh

Example
1. cd $HOME/QMMMWsoftware/examples
2. cd 32water_mc
3. ./job.sh

References
[1] C. Ma et al., Comp. Phys. Comm. 195 (2015) 191-198.
  QMMMW: A wrapper for QM/MM simulations with Quantum ESPRESSO  and LAMMPS
  Computer Physics Communications
  Volume 195, October 2015, Pages 191-198.
